              Lovosis specializes in building IT infrastructures that grow with your business. Our solutions provide secure, scalable, and high-performance networks that ensure uninterrupted operations, robust data protection, and future-ready technology.
            </p>
          </div>
          <figure class="overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/pictures/logo1.jpg" alt="Image description" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </figure>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="card sticky top-32 pt-4 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-600 rounded-lg shadow-xl cursor-pointer transition-all duration-300" id="card_1">
        <div class="card__content grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 p-5 rounded-lg text-left relative">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-light dark:text-neutral-200">Cloud Computing Solutions for Modern Enterprises</h2>
            <p class="text-base font-light leading-normal dark:text-neutral-300 mt-10">
              Transform the way you work with Lovosis' cloud computing services. We offer efficient cloud migration, data storage, and management solutions that ensure your business remains agile, collaborative, and accessible anytime, anywhere.
            </p>
          </div>
          <figure class="overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/pictures/logo2.jpg" alt="Image description" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
          </figure>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="card sticky top-32 pt-4 bg-white dark:bg-neutral-600 rounded-lg shadow-xl cursor-pointer transition-all duration-300" id="card_1">
        <div class="card__content grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 p-5 rounded-lg text-left relative">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-light dark:text-neutral-200">Advanced Data Analytics for Smarter Decision-Making</h2>
            <p class="text-base font-light leading-normal dark:text-neutral-300 mt-10">
              Unlock the power of data with Lovosis. Our advanced analytics solutions help you harness actionable insights, optimize operations, and make informed decisions that drive growth and innovation in your business.
            </p>
          </div>
          <figure class="overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/pictures/logo3.jpg" alt="Image description" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
